# Interview video — pick ONE primary option (optional: a default Forbes embed
# from the main site is used when these are unset).
#
# 1) YouTube (watch URL, youtu.be, or 11-char video id). We embed via
#    youtube-nocookie with modest branding (YouTube UI cannot be fully removed).
# VITE_FORBES_VIDEO=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xxxxxxxxxxx
#
# 2) Self-hosted MP4/WebM — feels fully native on your site (recommended for “our player” look).
# VITE_FORBES_VIDEO_MP4=https://your-cdn.com/path/forbes-interview.mp4
#
# 3) Any other embeddable page (Forbes player, etc.) — full iframe src:
# VITE_FORBES_VIDEO_EMBED_URL=https://...
